ğŸ§  10. Top Memory-Consuming Processes
âœ… Script:
#!/bin/bash
ps aux --sort=-%mem | head -n 10
ğŸ§  Explanation:
â€¢	Lists all processes sorted by memory usage.
â€¢	Top 10 most resource-hungry processes.
â€¢	Great for identifying performance bottlenecks.

